title: Donald Trump says his older sister isn’t interested in becoming a Supreme Court judge
text: Donald Trump says that if he becomes president, he would love to nominate his older sister — a federal circuit court judge — to the U.S. Supreme Court but that she probably would not be interested in the position. " I would love to, but I think she would be the one to say, 'No way, no way,' " Trump said in an interview […] ...
